ACL CONFIGURATION
-----------------
EN
CONF T
HO R1
INT G0/0
IP ADD 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.0
N SH
INT G0/1
IP ADD 10.0.0.1 255.255.255.0
N SH
END


EN
CONF T
IP DHCP POOL LAN
NETWORK 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.O
DEFAULT-ROUTER 192.168.1.1
END


IP ROUTE 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.0.0.2


ISP
---
EN
CONF T
HO ISP
INT G0/0
IP ADD 10.0.0.2 255.255.255.0
N SH
INT G0/1
IP ADD 100.0.0.1 255.255.255.0
N SH
END


EN
CONF T
IP ROUTE 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.0 10.0.0.1
END


CONFIGURING ACL
----------------
R1
----
EN
CONF T
ACCESS-LIST 130 DENY TCP 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 HOST 100.0.0.100 EQ 80
ACCESS-LIST 130 DENY TCP 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 HOST 100.0.0.100 EQ 22
ACCESS-LIST 130 DENY TCP 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 HOST 100.0.0.100 EQ SMTP
ACCESS-LIST 130 PERMIT IP ANY ANY



EN
CONF T
INT G0/0
IP ACCESS-GROUP 130 IN
END



Standard ACL CONFIGURATION
--------------------------


EN
CONFIG T
ACCESS-LIST 1 
^exitip dhcp pool vlan10network 192.168.20.0 255.255.255.0default-router 192.168.
^exitip dhcp pool vlan10network 192.168.20.0 255.255.255.0default-router 192.168.
